05(6005唔需要特登買，成本價貴)+5n11/5p71(唔建議5p71,如果要嘅不如買502再搭P100綿抵啲)+501蓋<br />\n例如：6200+6001CN+5n11+501 我見100已經有一set<br />\n而且 就算唔用5n11同501蓋 都ok 6001CN一對最平$30，我見$50通常都有<br />\n6003貴少少 $70成平價(睇你有冇運見到)<br />\n以上都可以頂到TG，但記得聞到味要即換<br />\n<br />\n想了解更多快啲入去連登睇啦😛<br />\n...<br />\n防毒面具篇完<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666931</a>"},{"pid":"f15f1668c923cea0705c41a16e509c6e7cb734a3","tid":1666813,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"db32158be246473bb56297ec4d11763ca4fd4fd9","tid":1666813,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:32:40.000Z","msg":"邊方面嘅嘢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:03:50.000Z","msg":"手袋 衫"},{"pid":"e866724850478d0bb9fcbed015a1142cdc0d169b","tid":1666813,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f15f1668c923cea0705c41a16e509c6e7cb734a3","tid":1666813,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"db32158be246473bb56297ec4d11763ca4fd4fd9","tid":1666813,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:32:40.000Z","msg":"邊方面嘅嘢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:03:50.000Z","msg":"手袋 衫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T22:42:04.000Z","msg":"不如你講有咩牌子想買再check <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"799947372e4e37a92d73cad83323f31096bfc987","tid":1666813,"uid":10973,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T00:53:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2915133/org/97fe0389791ff6f6972ba61eac23f948.jpg/DwPJtQOaN5c7zqaS9V2uVpPprydfocNUK7fHESu3xxE?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2915133%2Forg%2F97fe0389791ff6f6972ba61eac23f948.jpg%2FDwPJtQOaN5c7zqaS9V2uVpPprydfocNUK7fHESu3xxE%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=63ab9d03&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"156bb60a9572236ea4874f695f80e62ce631b4e5","tid":1666813,"uid":47239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"